# AssetFlow

Enterprise Asset & Resource Management System

## Technology

- Odoo 19
- Python 3.11
- PostgreSQL 17

## Features

- Department Management
- Employee Directory
- Asset Registration
- Asset Allocation
- Asset Transfer
- Resource Booking
- Maintenance Workflow
- Asset Audit
- Dashboard
- Notifications

